    • Method Detail

      • onCommonChargerStateChargingInfoUpdate

        void onCommonChargerStateChargingInfoUpdate(ARCOMMANDS_COMMON_CHARGERSTATE_CHARGINGINFO_PHASE_ENUM phase,
                                            ARCOMMANDS_COMMON_CHARGERSTATE_CHARGINGINFO_RATE_ENUM rate,
                                            byte intensity,
                                            byte fullChargingTime)
        Called when a command ChargingInfo of class ChargerState in project Common is decoded
        Parameters:
        _phase - The current charging phase.
        _rate - The charge rate. If phase is DISCHARGING, refers to the last charge.
        _intensity - The charging intensity, in dA. (12dA = 1,2A) ; If phase is DISCHARGING, refers to the last charge. Equals to 0 if not known.
        _fullChargingTime - The full charging time estimated, in minute. If phase is DISCHARGING, refers to the last charge. Equals to 0 if not known.
